      "name": "Applicability constraint: non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw, ASTM F1717 static loading only",
      "description": "This credibility assessment applies exclusively to non-cannulated pedicle screws with nominal outer diameter 7.5 mm and thread pitch 2.75 mm fabricated from Ti-6Al-4V ELI (ASTM F136). The FEA model and validation evidence are not applicable to cannulated variants, screws with outer diameter outside 7.0–8.0 mm, dynamic fatigue loading regimes, or polyaxial head configurations. Extension to any out-of-scope geometry or loading condition requires a new or amended COU with re-evaluated credibility factors."
    },
    "hasOperatingEnvelope": {
