      "description": "Valid operating range: axial compressive load 0–2500 N applied at 10 mm/min crosshead displacement rate; rod diameter 5.5 mm cobalt-chromium alloy; UHMWPE test block per ASTM F1717 Annex A1 (density 935–945 kg/m³, elastic modulus 0.9–1.1 GPa); screw insertion torque 8.0 ± 0.5 N·m; ambient temperature 20–25 °C; relative humidity 40–60%. Construct geometry: 100 mm rod segment between screw centroids ± 2 mm. Predictions outside these bounds have not been validated and must not be used without additional evidence."
    }
